never seen in the history

00:52:47.350 --> 00:52:49.040
of searching for human origins,

00:52:49.040 --> 00:52:50.610
complete femurs and stuff.

00:52:50.610 --> 00:52:53.910
I'm making them push the
technology before I will touch

00:52:53.910 --> 00:52:55.780
that, to try and extract them.

00:52:55.780 --> 00:52:58.620
To try and make programs that
will actually see into this

00:52:58.620 --> 00:53:00.750
and extract them in a quality
that we can use.

00:53:00.750 --> 00:53:04.730
Because it might be the last
time this happens.

00:53:04.730 --> 00:53:06.550
And if we don't invent that
technology, who's

00:53:06.550 --> 00:53:07.260
going to invent it?

00:53:07.260 --> 00:53:11.560
And you need something big
enough to drive the kind of

00:53:11.560 --> 00:53:14.215
R&amp;D that it takes to push the
field in a direction.

00:53:14.215 --> 00:53:15.579
And this is big enough.

